README.md
     7→# Soluna
     9→[中文](./README.zh-CN.md)
    10→
    11→[Live Examples](https://cloudwu.github.io/soluna/)
    12→
    13→A framework you can use to make 2D games in Lua with multithreading, living on Windows, Linux, macOS and modern Browsers (via WebAssembly).
    14→
    15→It is built on top of [sokol](https://github.com/floooh/sokol) and leverages the power of ltask for multithreading.
    16→
    17→[![Nightly](/../../actions/workflows/nightly.yml/badge.svg)](/../../actions/workflows/nightyly.yml)
    18→
